Installation

	Download and unpack the latest Solr release from the Apache download mirrors.

Start Solr

	$ bin/solr start            # this starts solr
	$ bin/solr create -c demo   # this creates a document collection called "demo"

Verify Solr Running or not?

	To verify itâ€™s up and running,you can point your browser at the admin page

	http://localhost:8983/solr/